APPLY FOR BENEFITS
The following steps outline the process of submitting an application in Family Hub.
To expedite the application process, add students to your account before applying.
To apply for free and reduced meals, navigate to Family Hub > Benefits > Apply.
On the Dashboard
1. Click Apply on the navigation bar or click Apply for Benefits
The Apply for Free or Reduced Benefits page displays.

